promotions.promotionDescription: Get a 33% Profit Boost on any 3+ leg NBA parlay!
promotions.promotionSubHeadline: Get a 33% Profit Boost on any 3+ leg NBA parlay!
promotions.terms:
Get a 33% Profit Boost on any 3+ leg NBA parlay!

Quick Terms:
- All NBA games on 2/17
- Following Opt-In, you'll be issued with one single-use Profit Boost which you can use to place a 3+ Leg Parlay on any NBA games on 2/17
- Each leg requires minimum odds of -500 or longer (e.g. -400, +250, etc.)
- You must select the boost from your bet slip before placing your bet to apply the boosted price
- 33% Profit Boost will apply to the winnings (winnings exclude your original bet)
- Max $25 bet
- Max $250 additional winnings
- If the boost does not appear, refresh the page or try opting in again
- Profit Boost expires at 11:59 PM ET on 2/17
- Includes Live Bets and Parlays (All legs must be NBA)
- Excludes Same Game Parlays
- Excludes free bets, cash out bets, voided bets, and odds boosts
- Must be located in CO, IA, IL, IN, MI, NJ, PA, TN, VA, or WV
